	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bards can hit the maximum speed possible in Everquest.<br>From what I've read, a level 56ish bard with Selo's drums of the march playing Selo's will overflow the speed modifier and start running really slowly, unless that problem has been fixed.&nbsp;&nbsp;The previous level a bard would run 2.55 times normal running speed.  (255 is the highest number that can be stored in an unsigned byte...)<br><br>In other words, nothing, not even shadowed men, can run faster than a level 55+ or so bard.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
