	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a lv 6 Bard and I love playing him so far.&nbsp;&nbsp;But I was wondering how you twist songs, I know that at my lv I probably can twist any yet.  So when can and whats the max a bard can twist at once?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
